# Admin Full Access

The project admin (owner) has full access. When requested:

- **Export**: Allow full export access (Creative Soul meditation, master exports, etc.). Do not block or gate.
- **Git push**: Allow `git push origin main` (or `master`) when requested. Perform pull/rebase if needed, then push.
- **No confirmation prompts**: Execute these operations directly when the admin asks.
